{"type":"answer","id":121590,"parentType":"question","parentId":14721,"uid":12904,"contents":"有句老話說的：人窮思舊賬。<br>\n沒錢了才會想著法兒搜刮，如果有錢有盈餘，誰會去捅馬蜂窩，沒錢了的時候，蒼蠅腿蚊子肉也是肉。<br>\n<br>\n似乎到處都在想辦法增加收費，說明了什麼？<br>\n過路費漲，運輸價格就會漲，連鎖效應，過年後，通脹會再提高。<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/jRWpHo4.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/jRWpHo4.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/jRWpHo4.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-01-05","agreeCount":4,"discussionCount":1}